Statement regarding Thuja Capital Fund Project by the UIF Labour Activation Program 31 December 2022 The Minister of Employment and Labour, TW Nxesi, notes the media reports on Thuja Capital Fund Project. This is a project under Labour Activation Programme (LAP), run by Unemployment Insurance Fund (UIF) together with some partners. “I have since instructed the Director General (DG) of the Department of Employment and Labour (DEL) and UIF Commissioner to suspend this project pending a full report on all the matters that are raised about it in media reports and related matters.” Statement issued by Ministry of Employment and Labour, 31 December 2022